research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:955:research/history/round_summaries/round_0183.json:21:    "summary": "已新增 low-cost prototype `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`：用 full-dim shared coarse sparse stage 先吃主干，再让 routed experts 只做 residual cleanup，并完成 config whitelist、factory dispatch 与 AutoResearch override allowlist 接线。建议下一轮以 r165 为 reference，仅切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`，在与当前 best `<0.25x` anchor 相同的 `K=108, EF=1` recipe 下做一次干净的 matched-cost architecture probe。该 family 的本地 exact smoke、override 校验、config-resolution 校验均已通过，成本自检为 `0.13x + 0.11x = 0.24x`，正好回答当前主问题：显式“shared 主干 + residual experts”分工能否在 low-cost 主战场打败现有 joint shared+routed anchor。",
