research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1365:research/history/round_summaries/round_0208.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r\uff1b{u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002r207 \u5df2\u7ecf\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk K=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160 TRUNK_RANK=16` \u63a8\u5230 objective=0.396871\u3001cost=0.199219x\u3001exceed=0.197653\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u70b9\u4e0e incumbent r199 \u7684\u5dee\u8ddd 0.010757 \u91cc\uff0c\u7edd\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u6765\u81ea cost \u800c\u4e0d\u662f exceed\uff1b\u540c\u65f6 family \u5185\u5df2\u6709\u65c1\u8bc1 r175 vs r170 \u8868\u660e\u5728\u66f4\u9ad8 K\u3001\u66f4\u5bbd latent \u7684 recipe \u4e0a\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 16 \u538b\u5230 8 \u80fd\u4ee5\u66f4\u4f4e cost \u6362\u6765\u66f4\u4f4e objective\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u5fc5\u7136\u9020\u6210 tail error \u7206\u70b8\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r207 \u4ec5\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 16 \u538b\u5230 8\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u7528\u66f4\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 trunk \u76f4\u63a5\u62b9\u6389\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u8981\u7531 encoder cost \u5e26\u6765\u7684 objective \u7f3a\u53e3\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\uff0c`TRUNK_RANK=16 -> 8` \u4f1a\u628a combined_accesses \u4ece 835584 \u964d\u5230 778240\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u7684 actual total_cost_ratio \u4ece\u7ea6 0.199219x \u964d\u5230\u7ea6 0.185547x\uff1b\u8fd9\u610f\u5473\u7740\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u7684\u56de\u5f39\u4e0d\u8d85\u8fc7\u7ea6 0.0137\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u5c31\u4f1a\u4f18\u4e8e r207\uff0c\u800c\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u4e0d\u9ad8\u4e8e\u7ea6 0.2006\uff0c\u5c31\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u8d8a\u8fc7 incumbent r199\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1385:research/history/round_summaries/round_0171.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 仍为 `lowrank_expert_topk`。最终重构公式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`：其中 `{u_r}` 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，`{b_{e,i}}` 是静态 expert 子库原子；在线侧只需要计算 trunk 系数 `β_r(x)`、轻量 router 选出少量 expert，再在被选中的静态子库内做有限加权和。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表/加权和 + routed 子库查表 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 frontier。r170 已在 `<0.25x` 主战场上给出一个有价值信号：`lowrank_expert_topk` 在约 `0.24x` total_cost 下做到 `FVU=0.1404`，虽然尚未击败 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=112` 的 `0.1369`，但已明显接近，说明这条“轻 trunk + routed expert、无 residual cleanup”路线并未被证伪。当前最值得回答的单一问题不是继续回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做更低信息量的局部细扫，而是：`lowrank_expert_topk` 能否在更低成本下仍维持对 low-cost anchors 的竞争力。故本轮以 r170 为 reference，只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 `224` 压到 `160`，其余 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, adam, LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接测试更小 per-expert width 是否能把该 family 从约 `0.24x` 压到约 `0.21x`，并在相近或更低成本下挑战当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 `0.20x-0.22x` 前沿段。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1391:research/history/round_summaries/round_0112.json:53:    "architecture": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1395:research/history/round_summaries/round_0112.json:133:    "architecture": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0217.stdout.log:1417:research/history/round_summaries/round_0083.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + residual 查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r79 与 r81 已表明继续动 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或继续压 `TRUNK_RANK` 会退化，r82 又表明在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上把 expert 粒度压粗到 16 会明显变差；因此当前最值得回答的问题是：在保留 residual cleanup 的三段式主线里，更粗的 expert 粒度是否仍然可行。相对 r76 只把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 64 降到 16，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变时，直接测试 residual 分支是否足以弥补更粗 expert 划分带来的局部容量损失，并在几乎不增部署成本的前提下把 selection cost 再向左推一小段。如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的粗 expert 失败主要因为缺少 residual cleanup，那么这个三段式 family 仍有机会在低到中成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。",
