research/history/logs/agent_round_0231.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(h(x)) b_{e,j} + Σ_m γ_m(r(x)) c_m`，其中 `h(x)=Bx` 是共享低维 bottleneck，`U={u_i}` 是 shared 静态库，`{B_e}` 是 routed expert 静态子库，`C={c_m}` 是 residual 静态补偿库，`r(x)` 是前两段重构后的残差。在线导出链路仍是“shared bottleneck 投影 + shared/routed 子库查表 + residual cleanup 查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性在线补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`shared_routed_expert_topk` 等仍属兼容 family；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属 `不兼容`，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：Round 229 与 Round 230 已经证明 residual cleanup 的确能明显压低 exceed，但当前未决问题变成“这种收益是否必须依赖昂贵的 full-dim trunk / scorer，还是更轻的 factorized shared+routed selector 也能保住大部分收益”。因此相对 r212 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_topk` 切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余主 recipe 不变，直接裁决“lighter scorer/router + residual cleanup”这条结构槽位本身值不值得继续。本地精确成本复核显示该点 selection_accesses=1490944、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=1654784，对当前 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy 的 exact total_cost_ratio=0.39453125；若要刷新 r212 的 objective=0.35553750753402713，需要 exceed_alpha_0.50 压到约 `≤-0.03899374246597288`，这在数学上已不现实。因此这不是近端翻盘点，而是一轮高信息量结构裁决：如果它无法在显著更低成本下保住 Round 229/230 已看到的低 exceed，则 factorized shared+routed residual 线在当前 target 上也应整体降级。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual@K32` 的 exceed 仍明显高于 Round 229 的 `0.160599`，则说明更轻 factorized shared+routed selector 守不住 residual-cleanup 收益；后续应整体下调这条线，而不是继续补 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或相关近邻插值。","如果该 probe 的 exceed 接近 Round 230 的 `0.171988` 但 cost 明显更低，说明 residual cleanup 的主要价值并不依赖 full-dim trunk；后续只在允许回到 param-only 压缩轴时，才值得围绕这条线测试更小 `K` 或更窄 factorized hidden。","如果该 probe 意外在 cost≈0.395x 下把 exceed 压到接近 `0.13~0.15`，则说明 lighter scorer/router 的确能保住一部分 cleanup 收益；下一轮才值得继续留在该 family 内做单参数 follow-up。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 229 `lowrank_expert_residual@K32` 给出 `objective=0.602006 / cost=0.441406x / exceed=0.160599 / fvu=0.134527`，说明 trunk + routed expert + residual cleanup 能明显压低 exceed，但交换率不足以支撑 objective。","Round 230 `two_stage_residual_expert@K32` 给出 `objective=0.586051 / cost=0.414062x / exceed=0.171988 / fvu=0.146965`，说明去掉 trunk 后仍有 cleanup 收益，但不如 `lowrank_expert_residual`。","single-library selector closure probes已完成且均为强负信号：`jumprelu@K32`、`group_topk@K32`、`topk@K32` 全都停在 `objective≈0.60 / cost=0.289062x / exceed≈0.31`。","本轮选择 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 的原因是：在 remaining compatible families 里，它最直接回答“更轻 scorer/router 能否保住 residual-cleanup 收益”这一当前最高信息量问题，且 exact total_cost 低于 `lowrank_expert_residual` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert`。","本地 allowlist 校验通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key: ARCHITECTURE, value: shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual}], fallback_architecture='expert_topk')` 返回空列表。","本地成本复核：`shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual K=32 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的 exact total_cost_ratio=0.39453125，其中 selection=0.35546875x、deployment=0.0390625x。"],"reference_round":212,"self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r212 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，没有新增参数，也没有代码改动。没有继续选 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，因为它在当前 matched recipe 下更贵；也没有回到 `whitened_topk` 或 `codebook_topk`，因为它们虽然未在当前 anchor recipe 上完整裁决，但与当前 residual-cleanup 归因问题相比信息增量更低。选择 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 的风险同样明确：它不可能刷新 incumbent，因此只能作为结构裁决，而不是 frontier attack；但在 Round 229/230 之后，这正是当前 remaining search space 里最值得回答的问题。","summary":"建议以 r212 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`。这轮的目标不是直接赢过 incumbent，而是判断 residual-cleanup 的收益能否在更轻的 factorized shared+routed 选择链路下保留下来，从而决定这条结构线是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
