research/history/logs/agent_round_0306_repair_1.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终实验假设不变：`shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 仍表示 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{j∈S_{e1(r1)}^τ(r1)} β_j c_{e1,j} + 1[ρ(r1-expert1_only(r1)) > 0.5·ρ(r1)] · Σ_{m∈S_{e2(r1)}^τ(r2)} γ_m c_{e2,m}`，并导出到 LUTurbo 的“shared 查表 + 条件级联 PK expert cleanup + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”链路；本次 repair 只修复工程阻塞，不改变 family 或 env patch。阻塞根因是 bare sanity config `SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1)` 未显式传 `active_experts` 时会落到全局默认值 1，而该 family 作为 ordered two-expert cascade 必须要求 2。已在实现中补上 family-local 默认：当 `cfg.active_experts is None` 时自动设为 2，再沿原有 cascade 逻辑初始化，从而让 exact launch string 的 sanity 构造不再失败。","summary":"已实际修复 `shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 sanity 阻塞，且没有改 family_name 或 env_overrides。最小补丁只落在 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`：为 cascade 家族在未显式传参时补齐 `active_experts=2` 的 family-local 默认。修复后，失败时同一条 bare-config sanity 命令和同一 `(architecture, K=32, EF=1)` integration smoke 都已本地通过。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这次 repair 没有重新设计实验，也没有改 family 或 override；只修了导致 sanity_failed 的最小实现缺口。风险主要在于这只是实例化阻塞修复，不代表结构效果已经被验证；但当前要求正是让原始实验能跑通，而这一步已经完成。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["repair 根因已确认：`shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 继承 ordered two-expert cascade 语义，但 bare config 未显式传 `active_experts` 时会走全局默认 1，导致构造器在 sanity 阶段报 `requires active_experts=2`。","已实际落盘最小修复：在 `SharedCascadeProductKeyExpertJumpReLUSparseCoder.__init__` 中，当 `cfg.active_experts is None` 时自动设为 2；这样 `shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 也继承到正确默认。","失败 payload 中的 exact sanity 命令已本地复跑通过：输出 `sanity: OK cuda 2`。","按架构集成清单复跑 exact-string smoke 已通过：`integration_smoke: OK shared_conditional_cascade_product_key_expert_jumprelu 32 1 cuda`。","本次 repair 未改 family_name、未改 env_overrides、未新增 tunable key，也未触碰 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh` wiring。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 round 306 修复后正常进入训练，则先看它是否真的把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到足以击败 r305，而不是立刻再开新结构。","如果修复后仍失败，下一轮应只围绕新的失败模式做工程修补，不要改 family 或 override。","如果训练能跑通但 objective 没赢，再根据实际 cost/exceed 分解决定是否继续保留这条 conditional cascade 支线。"],"reference_round":305}
